Preconfigured Claude skills and agents. Meant for my own personal use. Skills, agents, etc... are very opinonated and not meant to be generic.

Inspired by (and some content copied from):

- https://github.com/ChrisWiles/claude-code-showcase
- https://github.com/diet103/claude-code-infrastructure-showcase
- https://github.com/basher83/lunar-claude/tree/main/plugins/infrastructure/ansible-workflows/skills
- https://github.com/wshobson/agents/tree/main/plugins/frontend-mobile-development/skills/tailwind-design-system
- https://github.com/miles990/claude-software-skills/tree/main/programming-languages/shell-bash
- https://github.com/chongdashu/phaserjs-oakwoods/tree/main/.claude/skills/phaser-gamedev

To install or use the plugins:
/plugin marketplace add jbaranski/jeff-claude
/plugin install jeff-plugin-typescript@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-angular@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-python@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-aws-solution-architect@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-golang@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-ansible@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-frontend@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-shell-bash@jeff-plugins
/plugin install jeff-plugin-phaser@jeff-plugins

NOTE: The repo is public just so I can easily download and consume the skills quickly from any machine. The content is dervied from other sources and in some cases modified to be tailored for my needs. I am not trying to take "credit" or pass this off as my own.
